              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "Additive change only: existing rows gain a SECOND key hint. Where a destination has both a Super/Meta accelerator and a g-leader sequence, the row shows two hints; where it has only a sequence, it shows one. Same .cmdk-keys style (muted monospace) throughout — no new component.",
